Kali/Alecto:


Kali and Alecto continued firing against Slayer (25 shoots x 
bot). "We're loosing them" said the femme by a secret frecuency to 
Legder and Drillbit.


> ::Slayer::
> 
> Slayer continues to gain altitude and fly quickly south, dodging 
most of the shots fired at him from his followers. He was starting to 
lose them, increasing his speed and hoping that they didn't do the 
same. His scanners reported a base somewhere south, a very large one 
from the strengh of the energy signature. They also reported a bot 
approaching from behind, and by the time the gattling gun was fired, 
Slayer manages to dodge most of it, the blast blowing off one of his 
back feet.
> 
> He looks back at the three bots behind him, growling and heading a 
bit to the left, flying above ocean now, continuing to head south.
>
